<h3 id="key-ideas">Key Ideas</h3>

<p>â€¢ The basic metric for location is the mean, but it can be sensitive to
extreme values (outlier). â€¢ Other metrics (median, trimmed mean) are
less sensitive to outliers and unusual distributions and hence are more
robust.</p>
:ET